HEADWORD: Featured
<hw>Fea"tured</hw> <pr>(?; 135)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Shaped; fashioned.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How noble, young, how rarely <qex>featured</qex>!</q>
